### 1. First Message: Introduction & Session Initialization
# @name sendMessage1
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Hello, my name is Sogand and I am developing a Flask project."
}

###

### 2. Second Message: Testing Context Retention (Cookies are handled automatically)
# @name sendMessage2
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "What was my name and what project was I building?"
}

###

### 3. Third Message: Testing Continuous Memory Expansion
# @name sendMessage3
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "My project execution team consists of 4 people."
}